## Dataset Interning / Reuse


This page intentionally mixes page-level and viz-level `data` inputs.

## Uses page-level data

```{r uses-page-level-data}
# Uses page-level data
result <- tryCatch({
  viz_scatter(
    data = data,
    title = "Uses page-level data",
    color_palette = NULL,
    x_var = "age",
    y_var = "score",
    backend = "echarts4r"
  )
}, error = function(e) {
  stop("Visualization failed ('Uses page-level data', type 'scatter'): ", conditionMessage(e), call. = FALSE)
})

result
```
